[{"title":"hexo common commands","url":"/2021/04/24/hexo-common-commands/","content":"<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files-amp-amp-Run-server-amp-amp-Deploy\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files-amp-amp-Run-server-amp-amp-Deploy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files &amp;&amp; Run server &amp;&amp; Deploy\"></a>Generate static files &amp;&amp; Run server &amp;&amp; Deploy</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo s</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>","categories":["hexo"],"tags":["hexo"]}]